ygData.messageBody:
On the subject of camping for stuff, I'm proposing a trip to Runnyeyes. The
wiz can get the Blacken Medallion. The fighters type can get BI armors. Monks
and the rest can get pieces too to sell to ppl. Alot of ppl like BI armor (the
AC is worst and heavier than Banded stuff. Things ppl do for fashion.......) but
BI armor are magical so the only pieces I want is the gloves, boots and the
crown. The BI armor fits all races. and all fighter types can wear except Monk
(as usual). So u guys wanna come along this Sat? only lvl 20 and above. The
lower lvls will die very fast. And dangerous for 20plus too.
